longBusinessSummary: The index is designed to track the performance of a selection of companies from global developed and emerging markets engaged in the following themes (Artificial Intelligence) and its sub-themes (Deep learning, Image recognition, Natural language processing, Speech recognition & chatbots). The fund will invest at least 80% of its total assets (but typically far more) in component securities of the underlying index. The fund is non-diversified.
longName: Xtrackers Artificial Intelligence and Big Data ETF
